<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div><div><span style="line-height: 1.38; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></div><div><span style="line-height: 1.38; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Our BSF Director of Mandarin, Zhang Lijing, formerly Director of Mandarin at Harrow School Beijing and also at the British School of Beijing, will be spending the final 2 weeks of this academic year at BSKL training our staff on our new Mandarin curriculum. She will be joined by </span><span style="line-height: 1.38; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Zhao Xi coming to us</span><span style="line-height: 1.38; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> from Dulwich College Beijing who will lead the implementation of this new curriculum at BSKL in the next academic year.</span></div></div></div><div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="docs-internal-guid-739f9671-aa49-80e0-901b-21c29fb501ed"><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-71061b75-8f46-e682-427d-f33a91f56405"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"> </font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The new curriculum in many respects raises the bar in terms of aspiration and sets out clear pathways to fulfill different levels of fluency. First language speakers will have the opportunity to progress further more quickly and second language speakers who remain at BSKL for a number of years will have the opportunity to reach a high level of competency. Zhang Lijing will be holding parent information sessions on this new curriculum: </font></span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Primary parents: Tuesday 5th July 2pm in the Secondary Library </font></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Secondary parents (including Y6): Monday 11th July 15.40pm in the Theatre</font></b></span></p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">I look forward to introducing Zhang Lijing in person at these sessions.</span></font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div><br><p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Warm regards</font></span></p><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Janet Brock</span></font></span></div></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><b>Headteacher</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></span></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color